OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain on
OL,7,FSunday and Monday as winds strengthen,
OL,8,Fsome drier and brighter intervals
OL,9,Fpossible. Drier Tuesday with just the
OL,10,Fodd shower possible and sunny spells.
